    "For LLAMA2-7B-CHAT, VICUNA-7B-1.5, and MISTRAL-7B-INSTRUCT-0.2, we set the max iteration to be 1000, 100, and 500, respectively.",
    "We initialize the adversarial suffix with several possible initial strings.",
    "Table 5 provides a sensitivity analysis of different initial strings on ATLA.",
    "After optimization, we use the learned suffix to concatenate with future harmful questions.",
    "Then feed the resulting attack prompts to victim LLMs to get responses."
